{"tid":2197723,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"法國防長突訪印度 展軍火與地區戰略所圖","createTime":"2020-09-10T23:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T11:21:52.000Z","uid":7736,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"c9239da107af9f83c6db04dbf74ca27f503a54ee","tid":2197723,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T23:33:57.000Z","msg":"在新德里和北京之間緊張局勢加劇之際，法國國防部長佛羅倫薩&middot;帕里（Florence Parly）周四赴印度進行閃電之旅，以促進法國軍事工業發展。不過，法國指除了推銷軍火，也希望與印度在該地區推動外交與戰略合作。法國剛剛與印度以及澳大利亞首次召開了三國會議，推升在該地區的多方位合作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B/20200910-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%95%B7%E7%AA%81%E8%A8%AA%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6-%E5%B1%95%E8%BB%8D%E7%81%AB%E8%88%87%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E6%88%B0%E7%95%A5%E6%89%80%E5%9C%96?fbclid=IwAR2hOeT473U3Dqv1dNV0tWxOBlbV98RGmsLUaaLGwmq0uOT3_rk4khEGdRg&amp;ref=fb_i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Fcn%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%258B%2F20200910-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2598%25B2%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%25AA%2581%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6-%25E5%25B1%2595%25E8%25BB%258D%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%2595%25A5%25E6%2589%2580%25E5%259C%2596%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2hOeT473U3Dqv1dNV0tWxOBlbV98RGmsLUaaLGwmq0uOT3_rk4khEGdRg%26ref%3Dfb_i&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=305be902\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B/20200910-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%95%B7%E7%AA%81%E8%A8%AA%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6-%E5%B1%95%E8%BB%8D%E7%81%AB%E8%88%87%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E6%88%B0%E7%95%A5%E6%89%80%E5%9C%96?fbclid=IwAR2hOeT473U3Dqv1dNV0tWxOBlbV98RGmsLUaaLGwmq0uOT3_rk4khEGdRg&amp;ref=fb_i</a>"},{"pid":"5ca5f43a94ed4bb33a1afd63800ddc6818856882","tid":2197723,"uid":37596,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T23:37:18.000Z","msg":"全球支援印度打鳩支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2cd7e62cdb0edce7b0e22c4409416ee3f5f23f7","tid":219772